  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operation Supervisor",
  "description": "<p>1) Shall ensure the daily operations of various sites assigned and liaise with clients on the requirements </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2) Arrange for daily staff deployments to various sites and ensure company does not incur any liquidated damages on the projects </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3) Rostering of monthly schedules</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4) Coordinate with site in charge on backlog if any</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5) Rectify on site issues with workers or clients upon receiving feedback </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6) Reporting of daily attendance to head office and to submit and ensure timesheets are all in proper orders </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>7) Prepare monthly financial reports for various operations projects</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>8) Arrange for coverage in case of absence of staff and able to hands on in event of no coverage</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>9) Candidate must be independent and proactive to provide suggestions and solve problems with initiative</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>10) Candidate shall possess class 3 licence</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>11) Candidate shall respond to any business or projects assignment regardless of time in event of need</p>",
